Mark B. Grier



Mr. Mark B. Grier is on the Board of Directors at Prudential Financial, Inc., Wachovia Securities Financial Holdings LLC, The Prudential Variable Contract Real Property Account, and The Prudential Insurance Co. of America.
Mr. Grier was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer by The Prudential Insurance Co. of America, a Principal by The Chase Manhattan Corp., Treasurer by Lincoln First Banks, Inc., Senior Vice President by Lincoln First Bank N A, and Executive Vice President by The Chase Manhattan Bank NA.
He received his undergraduate degree from Eastern Illinois University, a graduate degree from Eastern Illinois University, and an MBA from the University of Rochester.



